[
  {
    "index": 1,
    "start": "0:00:02.23",
    "end": "0:00:28.29",
    "text": "And I stood upon the sand of the sea, and saw a Monster rise up out of the sea,"
  },
  {
    "index": 2,
    "start": "0:00:05.27",
    "end": "0:00:28.29",
    "text": "having seven heads and ten horns, and upon his horns ten crowns,"
  },
  {
    "index": 3,
    "start": "0:00:08.19",
    "end": "0:00:28.29",
    "text": "And upon his head the name of blasphemy (...)"
  },
  {
    "index": 4,
    "start": "0:00:11.19",
    "end": "0:00:28.29",
    "text": "And they worshiped the dragon which gave power unto the Monster:"
  },
  {
    "index": 5,
    "start": "0:00:14.20",
    "end": "0:00:28.29",
    "text": "and they worshiped the Monster, saying,"
  },
  {
    "index": 6,
    "start": "0:00:17.20",
    "end": "0:00:28.29",
    "text": "\"Who is like unto the Monster?"
  },
  {
    "index": 7,
    "start": "0:00:20.20",
    "end": "0:00:28.29",
    "text": "Who is able to make war with him?\""
  },
  {
    "index": 8,
    "start": "0:00:23.37",
    "end": "0:00:28.29",
    "text": "< The Black Book of Johann, Revelation 13, #1-4 > \n This is an actual passage from the Bible with the word \n \"beast\" replaced with \"monster,\" and \"Ioanes\" with \"Johann.\""
  },
  {
    "index": 9,
    "start": "0:00:36.82",
    "end": "0:00:38.07",
    "text": "That was amazing!"
  },
  {
    "index": 10,
    "start": "0:00:38.07",
    "end": "0:00:40.53",
    "text": "Yes, his skills are unmatched"
  },
  {
    "index": 11,
    "start": "0:00:40.53",
    "end": "0:00:44.99",
    "text": "I couldn't believe his speed, even when clipping \n that difficult cranial arterial mass!"
  },
  {
    "index": 12,
    "start": "0:00:44.99",
    "end": "0:00:45.95",
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "index": 13,
    "start": "0:00:45.95",
    "end": "0:00:48.91",
    "text": "That was a splendid operation, Herr Dr. Tenma."
  },
  {
    "index": 14,
    "start": "0:00:49.29",
    "end": "0:00:53.42",
    "text": "I finally got to see what a genius Kenzou \n Tenma is with my own eyes."
  },
  {
    "index": 15,
    "start": "0:00:53.96",
    "end": "0:00:56.38",
    "text": "No, it was all due to everyone's hard work."
  },
  {
    "index": 16,
    "start": "0:00:56.38",
    "end": "0:00:57.67",
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "index": 17,
    "start": "0:00:58.59",
    "end": "0:01:00.92",
    "text": "I can't believe the sun is so high already..."
  },
  {
    "index": 18,
    "start": "0:01:00.92",
    "end": "0:01:04.72",
    "text": "Well, we did operate for six hours straight."
  },
  {
    "index": 19,
    "start": "0:01:05.60",
    "end": "0:01:08.47",
    "text": "There aren't any other patients today, so rest up."
  },
  {
    "index": 20,
    "start": "0:01:36.96",
    "end": "0:01:39.12",
    "text": "Hey, where is daddy?"
  },
  {
    "index": 21,
    "start": "0:01:39.12",
    "end": "0:01:41.04",
    "text": "What happened to daddy?"
  },
  {
    "index": 22,
    "start": "0:03:21.51",
    "end": "0:03:25.47",
    "text": "Herr Dr. Tenma"
  },
  {
    "index": 23,
    "start": "0:03:26.47",
    "end": "0:03:30.89",
    "text": "Düsseldorf \n (Germany)"
  },
  {
    "index": 24,
    "start": "0:03:52.02",
    "end": "0:03:53.40",
    "text": "Come on, wake up already."
  },
  {
    "index": 25,
    "start": "0:03:52.19",
    "end": "0:03:55.40",
    "text": "Good morning.  This is the news at eight."
  },
  {
    "index": 26,
    "start": "0:03:54.11",
    "end": "0:03:55.98",
    "text": "Wake up, Dr. Tenma."
  },
  {
    "index": 27,
    "start": "0:03:55.50",
    "end": "0:03:58.92",
    "text": "Kenzou Tenma"
  },
  {
    "index": 28,
    "start": "0:03:55.40",
    "end": "0:03:58.69",
    "text": "We're here to bring you the following news."
  },
  {
    "index": 29,
    "start": "0:04:01.53",
    "end": "0:04:03.70",
    "text": "Don't you think the roles have been reversed?"
  },
  {
    "index": 30,
    "start": "0:04:02.01",
    "end": "0:04:05.37",
    "text": "Eva Heinemann"
  },
  {
    "index": 31,
    "start": "0:04:03.70",
    "end": "0:04:07.41",
    "text": "It should be a princess like myself being woken with a kiss."
  },
  {
    "index": 32,
    "start": "0:04:05.12",
    "end": "0:04:10.12",
    "text": "First, the widespread news about the East German \n Foreign Trade Adviser, Mr. Liebert."
  },
  {
    "index": 33,
    "start": "0:04:08.37",
    "end": "0:04:10.70",
    "text": "Oh, you are here, Eva?"
  },
  {
    "index": 34,
    "start": "0:04:10.12",
    "end": "0:04:12.08",
    "text": "Hello, Mr. Reimann from Düsseldorf."
  },
  {
    "index": 35,
    "start": "0:04:12.08",
    "end": "0:04:15.25",
    "text": "You forgot about our date, didn't you, Kenzou?"
  },
  {
    "index": 36,
    "start": "0:04:13.33",
    "end": "0:04:15.67",
    "text": "We're here in Düsseldorf."
  },
  {
    "index": 37,
    "start": "0:04:15.88",
    "end": "0:04:18.75",
    "text": "No, it's not that I forgot about it..."
  },
  {
    "index": 38,
    "start": "0:04:16.83",
    "end": "0:04:21.42",
    "text": "Now that the Foreign Trade Adviser who fled to West Germany..."
  },
  {
    "index": 39,
    "start": "0:04:21.42",
    "end": "0:04:27.30",
    "text": "Adviser Liebert made an appearance before the media with his family yesterday."
  },
  {
    "index": 40,
    "start": "0:04:27.55",
    "end": "0:04:30.01",
    "text": "Mr. Liebert, without any sign of fatigue on his face..."
  },
  {
    "index": 41,
    "start": "0:04:30.01",
    "end": "0:04:33.43",
    "text": "...along with his twin son and daughter..."
  },
  {
    "index": 42,
    "start": "0:04:33.43",
    "end": "0:04:36.10",
    "text": "...appeared, smiling brightly."
  },
  {
    "index": 43,
    "start": "0:04:36.10",
    "end": "0:04:40.44",
    "text": "His family is planning to stay here in Düsseldorf for some time..."
  },
  {
    "index": 44,
    "start": "0:04:40.44",
    "end": "0:04:43.73",
    "text": "...and carry on with their daily lives in an apartment provided by our TV station."
  },
  {
    "index": 45,
    "start": "0:04:45.11",
    "end": "0:04:46.86",
    "text": "I don't feel like I've slept at all..."
  },
  {
    "index": 46,
    "start": "0:04:45.15",
    "end": "0:04:47.03",
    "text": "Now, onto the next story."
  },
  {
    "index": 47,
    "start": "0:04:47.74",
    "end": "0:04:50.65",
    "text": "Hey, wake up!"
  },
  {
    "index": 48,
    "start": "0:04:49.11",
    "end": "0:04:51.95",
    "text": "The famous opera singer, Mr. Rosenbach..."
  },
  {
    "index": 49,
    "start": "0:04:50.65",
    "end": "0:04:51.86",
    "text": "This one is about you!"
  },
  {
    "index": 50,
    "start": "0:04:51.95",
    "end": "0:04:54.57",
    "text": "...collapsed yesterday due to an internal hemorrhage."
  },
  {
    "index": 51,
    "start": "0:04:54.57",
    "end": "0:04:57.37",
    "text": "He is reported to be in stable condition after surgery."
  },
  {
    "index": 52,
    "start": "0:04:57.37",
    "end": "0:05:01.33",
    "text": "Director Heinemann, from the Düsseldorf Eisler Memorial \n Hospital, participated in the operation..."
  },
  {
    "index": 53,
    "start": "0:05:01.33",
    "end": "0:05:04.29",
    "text": "...and held a press conference a short time ago."
  },
  {
    "index": 54,
    "start": "0:05:04.50",
    "end": "0:05:08.92",
    "text": "Mr. Rosenbach's diagnosis revealed that he suffered \n from a ruptured artery in the brain."
  },
  {
    "index": 55,
    "start": "0:05:08.92",
    "end": "0:05:11.17",
    "text": "The operation itself went accordingly."
  },
  {
    "index": 56,
    "start": "0:05:11.17",
    "end": "0:05:15.30",
    "text": "The clipping went extremely well, too."
  },
  {
    "index": 57,
    "start": "0:05:15.80",
    "end": "0:05:18.55",
    "text": "Mr. Rosenbach has numerous fans."
  },
  {
    "index": 58,
    "start": "0:05:18.55",
    "end": "0:05:19.85",
    "text": "Do you think he'll make a full recovery?"
  },
  {
    "index": 59,
    "start": "0:05:20.18",
    "end": "0:05:25.10",
    "text": "Yes, we'll put forth every effort \n to recover his singing voice."
  },
  {
    "index": 60,
    "start": "0:05:25.64",
    "end": "0:05:31.48",
    "text": "Dr. Heinemann's team has had success in \n numerous difficult operations to date."
  },
  {
    "index": 61,
    "start": "0:05:31.48",
    "end": "0:05:37.86",
    "text": "But with this operation, we can now say that they have \n secured their position in the medical world in our country."
  },
  {
    "index": 62,
    "start": "0:05:37.86",
    "end": "0:05:40.03",
    "text": "That is amazing, Kenzou!"
  },
  {
    "index": 63,
    "start": "0:05:40.03",
    "end": "0:05:41.86",
    "text": "The news wasn't about me..."
  },
  {
    "index": 64,
    "start": "0:05:41.86",
    "end": "0:05:43.70",
    "text": "It was about your father."
  },
  {
    "index": 65,
    "start": "0:05:43.70",
    "end": "0:05:45.08",
    "text": "That is true, but..."
  },
  {
    "index": 66,
    "start": "0:05:45.41",
    "end": "0:05:51.25",
    "text": "It's because you performed a perfect surgery \n with my father's team last night."
  },
  {
    "index": 67,
    "start": "0:05:50.29",
    "end": "0:05:51.25",
    "text": "In other news..."
  },
  {
    "index": 68,
    "start": "0:05:51.25",
    "end": "0:05:53.46",
    "text": "I'm sure father appreciates your efforts."
  },
  {
    "index": 69,
    "start": "0:05:53.46",
    "end": "0:05:56.79",
    "text": "You're responsible for improving the hospital's reputation."
  },
  {
    "index": 70,
    "start": "0:05:57.29",
    "end": "0:05:59.71",
    "text": "I'm the one who should be thankful..."
  },
  {
    "index": 71,
    "start": "0:05:59.71",
    "end": "0:06:04.68",
    "text": "...since it's thanks to your father that \n I can work like this in Germany."
  },
  {
    "index": 72,
    "start": "0:06:04.68",
    "end": "0:06:06.59",
    "text": "Good luck, Kenzou."
  },
  {
    "index": 73,
    "start": "0:06:06.59",
    "end": "0:06:09.05",
    "text": "I'm positive everything will work out fine \n if you follow in my father's footsteps."
  },
  {
    "index": 74,
    "start": "0:06:09.60",
    "end": "0:06:13.18",
    "text": "It's only matter of time before my father becomes the chief director."
  },
  {
    "index": 75,
    "start": "0:06:13.18",
    "end": "0:06:15.98",
    "text": "Then you'll soon be the head of the surgical department."
  },
  {
    "index": 76,
    "start": "0:06:15.98",
    "end": "0:06:18.06",
    "text": "And eventually, a director."
  },
  {
    "index": 77,
    "start": "0:06:19.60",
    "end": "0:06:22.36",
    "text": "That'll make me the wife of a director."
  },
  {
    "index": 78,
    "start": "0:06:22.36",
    "end": "0:06:23.98",
    "text": "You better make me happy..."
  },
  {
    "index": 79,
    "start": "0:06:23.98",
    "end": "0:06:26.07",
    "text": "...because hardship doesn't suit me."
  },
  {
    "index": 80,
    "start": "0:06:27.24",
    "end": "0:06:28.82",
    "text": "Should we leave?"
  },
  {
    "index": 81,
    "start": "0:06:28.82",
    "end": "0:06:30.16",
    "text": "Or should we..."
  },
  {
    "index": 82,
    "start": "0:06:31.86",
    "end": "0:06:36.12",
    "text": "...the southern region will be rainy over the weekend."
  },
  {
    "index": 83,
    "start": "0:06:39.29",
    "end": "0:06:41.54",
    "text": "Blood pressure, 128/64."
  },
  {
    "index": 84,
    "start": "0:06:41.96",
    "end": "0:06:42.87",
    "text": "Retractor."
  },
  {
    "index": 85,
    "start": "0:06:45.92",
    "end": "0:06:48.34",
    "text": "I'm going to make an incision in the pyramis now."
  },
  {
    "index": 86,
    "start": "0:06:55.13",
    "end": "0:06:58.76",
    "text": "That was a perfect operation as usual, Dr. Tenma!"
  },
  {
    "index": 87,
    "start": "0:06:58.76",
    "end": "0:07:00.31",
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "index": 88,
    "start": "0:07:00.44",
    "end": "0:07:03.02",
    "text": "Dr. Becker"
  },
  {
    "index": 89,
    "start": "0:07:00.43",
    "end": "0:07:03.31",
    "text": "Although it doesn't seem like you're \n only good at operating on people..."
  },
  {
    "index": 90,
    "start": "0:07:05.48",
    "end": "0:07:07.98",
    "text": "You hold the position of chief at such a young age..."
  },
  {
    "index": 91,
    "start": "0:07:07.98",
    "end": "0:07:10.40",
    "text": "...and both the director and the surgical head hold you in the high esteem."
  },
  {
    "index": 92,
    "start": "0:07:10.40",
    "end": "0:07:11.69",
    "text": "And on top of that..."
  },
  {
    "index": 93,
    "start": "0:07:11.69",
    "end": "0:07:15.03",
    "text": "...you won the heart of the director's daughter."
  },
  {
    "index": 94,
    "start": "0:07:15.23",
    "end": "0:07:18.45",
    "text": "What are you trying to say, Dr. Becker?"
  },
  {
    "index": 95,
    "start": "0:07:18.45",
    "end": "0:07:22.24",
    "text": "Sorry.  I don't mean anything bad."
  },
  {
    "index": 96,
    "start": "0:07:22.24",
    "end": "0:07:24.24",
    "text": "Because a hospital is just a world of politics."
  },
  {
    "index": 97,
    "start": "0:07:25.58",
    "end": "0:07:29.96",
    "text": "You know full well that you're being \n used by the director, right?"
  },
  {
    "index": 98,
    "start": "0:07:29.96",
    "end": "0:07:32.96",
    "text": "The operation that you performed \n successfully on the opera singer..."
  },
  {
    "index": 99,
    "start": "0:07:32.96",
    "end": "0:07:37.38",
    "text": "He held a press conference on TV \n as if he did everything himself."
  },
  {
    "index": 100,
    "start": "0:07:38.34",
    "end": "0:07:42.63",
    "text": "Although it means you have talent, if you're being used."
  },
  {
    "index": 101,
    "start": "0:07:42.63",
    "end": "0:07:45.43",
    "text": "When you get promoted, put in a good word for me."
  },
  {
    "index": 102,
    "start": "0:07:46.34",
    "end": "0:07:48.05",
    "text": "I'll treat you sometime, okay?"
  },
  {
    "index": 103,
    "start": "0:08:12.07",
    "end": "0:08:14.45",
    "text": "Umm, may I help you?"
  },
  {
    "index": 104,
    "start": "0:08:14.45",
    "end": "0:08:16.62",
    "text": "You're Dr. Tenma?"
  },
  {
    "index": 105,
    "start": "0:08:16.62",
    "end": "0:08:17.29",
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "index": 106,
    "start": "0:08:18.50",
    "end": "0:08:20.00",
    "text": "Give me back my husband."
  },
  {
    "index": 107,
    "start": "0:08:23.42",
    "end": "0:08:25.59",
    "text": "Give him back!"
  },
  {
    "index": 108,
    "start": "0:08:26.75",
    "end": "0:08:30.09",
    "text": "Why didn't you operate on my husband?!"
  },
  {
    "index": 109,
    "start": "0:08:30.09",
    "end": "0:08:31.21",
    "text": "Y-You are...?"
  },
  {
    "index": 110,
    "start": "0:08:31.51",
    "end": "0:08:35.39",
    "text": "My husband was brought into the hospital first!"
  },
  {
    "index": 111,
    "start": "0:08:35.39",
    "end": "0:08:38.85",
    "text": "He was brought in long before that stupid opera singer!"
  },
  {
    "index": 112,
    "start": "0:08:38.85",
    "end": "0:08:41.10",
    "text": "But you guys pushed him back!"
  },
  {
    "index": 113,
    "start": "0:08:42.64",
    "end": "0:08:46.27",
    "text": "Aren't you the most skilled doctor in this hospital?!"
  },
  {
    "index": 114,
    "start": "0:08:47.02",
    "end": "0:08:47.81",
    "text": "So why?"
  },
  {
    "index": 115,
    "start": "0:08:48.27",
    "end": "0:08:50.94",
    "text": "Why?!"
  },
  {
    "index": 116,
    "start": "0:08:51.90",
    "end": "0:08:53.61",
    "text": "It was then I recalled that...."
  },
  {
    "index": 117,
    "start": "0:08:55.11",
    "end": "0:08:59.03",
    "text": "I was going to operate on a Turkish man who \n got injured in a construction accident."
  },
  {
    "index": 118,
    "start": "0:08:59.91",
    "end": "0:09:01.57",
    "text": "Dr. Tenma!"
  },
  {
    "index": 119,
    "start": "0:09:01.57",
    "end": "0:09:02.32",
    "text": "Yes?"
  },
  {
    "index": 120,
    "start": "0:09:02.82",
    "end": "0:09:04.37",
    "text": "This isn't your operation."
  },
  {
    "index": 121,
    "start": "0:09:04.37",
    "end": "0:09:06.70",
    "text": "Hurry up and go to operating room #1."
  },
  {
    "index": 122,
    "start": "0:09:07.37",
    "end": "0:09:09.33",
    "text": "It's an order from the director."
  },
  {
    "index": 123,
    "start": "0:09:09.33",
    "end": "0:09:10.54",
    "text": "Please hurry!"
  },
  {
    "index": 124,
    "start": "0:09:12.42",
    "end": "0:09:15.63",
    "text": "If only you had operated on him, \n he would have survived!"
  },
  {
    "index": 125,
    "start": "0:09:15.63",
    "end": "0:09:16.42",
    "text": "If only you had...!"
  },
  {
    "index": 126,
    "start": "0:09:16.42",
    "end": "0:09:18.00",
    "text": "Mom!"
  },
  {
    "index": 127,
    "start": "0:09:18.21",
    "end": "0:09:20.05",
    "text": "Give him back!"
  },
  {
    "index": 128,
    "start": "0:09:20.05",
    "end": "0:09:21.47",
    "text": "Give him back..."
  },
  {
    "index": 129,
    "start": "0:09:20.71",
    "end": "0:09:22.80",
    "text": "Mom!"
  },
  {
    "index": 130,
    "start": "0:09:26.39",
    "end": "0:09:29.89",
    "text": "So my friend and I fought over that dress."
  },
  {
    "index": 131,
    "start": "0:09:29.89",
    "end": "0:09:31.72",
    "text": "They only had one dress of that size left."
  },
  {
    "index": 132,
    "start": "0:09:32.18",
    "end": "0:09:33.48",
    "text": "But you don't have to worry about anything."
  },
  {
    "index": 133,
    "start": "0:09:33.48",
    "end": "0:09:35.19",
    "text": "I made it mine in the end."
  },
  {
    "index": 134,
    "start": "0:09:36.89",
    "end": "0:09:38.52",
    "text": "Hey, are you listening to me?"
  },
  {
    "index": 135,
    "start": "0:09:41.15",
    "end": "0:09:42.52",
    "text": "Yeah..."
  },
  {
    "index": 136,
    "start": "0:09:42.52",
    "end": "0:09:44.11",
    "text": "What is wrong with you?"
  },
  {
    "index": 137,
    "start": "0:09:44.11",
    "end": "0:09:45.19",
    "text": "You seem out of it."
  },
  {
    "index": 138,
    "start": "0:09:45.78",
    "end": "0:09:47.74",
    "text": "I checked the medical records..."
  },
  {
    "index": 139,
    "start": "0:09:47.74",
    "end": "0:09:51.20",
    "text": "The one who operated on the \n Turkish man was Dr. Becker."
  },
  {
    "index": 140,
    "start": "0:09:51.82",
    "end": "0:09:54.08",
    "text": "Oh, come on.  You're still talking about that?"
  },
  {
    "index": 141,
    "start": "0:09:54.08",
    "end": "0:09:57.54",
    "text": "It's obvious that he took too much \n time to begin the treatment."
  },
  {
    "index": 142,
    "start": "0:09:57.54",
    "end": "0:10:00.00",
    "text": "If I were the one who had operated on him..."
  },
  {
    "index": 143,
    "start": "0:10:00.00",
    "end": "0:10:04.46",
    "text": "...maybe I could have saved that Turkish man's life."
  },
  {
    "index": 144,
    "start": "0:10:04.84",
    "end": "0:10:06.71",
    "text": "Stop it!  We're eating here!"
  },
  {
    "index": 145,
    "start": "0:10:06.84",
    "end": "0:10:09.55",
    "text": "But what does she want from me?"
  },
  {
    "index": 146,
    "start": "0:10:09.55",
    "end": "0:10:14.18",
    "text": "I only operated on the opera singer because \n the director ordered me to."
  },
  {
    "index": 147,
    "start": "0:10:14.18",
    "end": "0:10:15.72",
    "text": "It's not my fault."
  },
  {
    "index": 148,
    "start": "0:10:16.09",
    "end": "0:10:17.51",
    "text": "Don't you think so?"
  },
  {
    "index": 149,
    "start": "0:10:19.18",
    "end": "0:10:20.22",
    "text": "Of course."
  },
  {
    "index": 150,
    "start": "0:10:22.02",
    "end": "0:10:24.77",
    "text": "Because people's lives aren't equal."
  },
  {
    "index": 151,
    "start": "0:10:41.95",
    "end": "0:10:43.74",
    "text": "Give him back!"
  },
  {
    "index": 152,
    "start": "0:10:43.87",
    "end": "0:10:45.95",
    "text": "Give my husband back!"
  },
  {
    "index": 153,
    "start": "0:10:45.95",
    "end": "0:10:47.20",
    "text": "Give him back!"
  },
  {
    "index": 154,
    "start": "0:11:00.80",
    "end": "0:11:01.88",
    "text": "Is that the house?"
  },
  {
    "index": 155,
    "start": "0:11:01.88",
    "end": "0:11:04.09",
    "text": "Yes, the report was made by one of the neighbors."
  },
  {
    "index": 156,
    "start": "0:11:06.47",
    "end": "0:11:08.18",
    "text": "How many shots were fired?"
  },
  {
    "index": 157,
    "start": "0:11:08.18",
    "end": "0:11:09.56",
    "text": "Five or six, sir."
  },
  {
    "index": 158,
    "start": "0:11:09.56",
    "end": "0:11:10.81",
    "text": "Who lives in this house?"
  },
  {
    "index": 159,
    "start": "0:11:11.22",
    "end": "0:11:12.81",
    "text": "W-Well..."
  },
  {
    "index": 160,
    "start": "0:11:12.81",
    "end": "0:11:17.56",
    "text": "It's the house of Mr. Liebert, the trade adviser \n who fled from East Germany a few days ago."
  },
  {
    "index": 161,
    "start": "0:11:17.56",
    "end": "0:11:21.07",
    "text": "Oh, this is going to be a problem."
  },
  {
    "index": 162,
    "start": "0:11:26.36",
    "end": "0:11:29.24",
    "text": "We're going in on the count or three."
  },
  {
    "index": 163,
    "start": "0:11:29.24",
    "end": "0:11:30.24",
    "text": "One..."
  },
  {
    "index": 164,
    "start": "0:11:30.24",
    "end": "0:11:31.07",
    "text": "Two..."
  },
  {
    "index": 165,
    "start": "0:11:31.07",
    "end": "0:11:31.49",
    "text": "Three!"
  },
  {
    "index": 166,
    "start": "0:11:55.22",
    "end": "0:11:56.64",
    "text": "This is terrible..."
  },
  {
    "index": 167,
    "start": "0:11:56.64",
    "end": "0:11:58.18",
    "text": "Who could have..."
  },
  {
    "index": 168,
    "start": "0:12:01.68",
    "end": "0:12:03.43",
    "text": "S-Someone is there!"
  },
  {
    "index": 169,
    "start": "0:12:18.95",
    "end": "0:12:21.91",
    "text": "Survivor confirmed.  One young girl."
  },
  {
    "index": 170,
    "start": "0:12:21.91",
    "end": "0:12:23.41",
    "text": "A man and a woman are dead."
  },
  {
    "index": 171,
    "start": "0:12:23.41",
    "end": "0:12:25.37",
    "text": "A boy in critical condition."
  },
  {
    "index": 172,
    "start": "0:12:25.37",
    "end": "0:12:26.45",
    "text": "I repeat..."
  },
  {
    "index": 173,
    "start": "0:12:26.45",
    "end": "0:12:28.50",
    "text": "A boy in critical condition!"
  },
  {
    "index": 174,
    "start": "0:12:39.67",
    "end": "0:12:41.42",
    "text": "An emergency case?"
  },
  {
    "index": 175,
    "start": "0:12:47.27",
    "end": "0:12:48.19",
    "text": "A bullet in his head?"
  },
  {
    "index": 176,
    "start": "0:12:49.28",
    "end": "0:12:51.53",
    "text": "The boy is the only patient?"
  },
  {
    "index": 177,
    "start": "0:12:51.53",
    "end": "0:12:53.70",
    "text": "Yes, his parents died instantly."
  },
  {
    "index": 178,
    "start": "0:12:53.70",
    "end": "0:12:55.70",
    "text": "It appears to be a robbery of some kind."
  },
  {
    "index": 179,
    "start": "0:12:56.16",
    "end": "0:12:59.70",
    "text": "Okay, I'll be at the hospital in about five minutes."
  },
  {
    "index": 180,
    "start": "0:13:08.88",
    "end": "0:13:10.29",
    "text": "Oh, father."
  },
  {
    "index": 181,
    "start": "0:13:11.17",
    "end": "0:13:16.46",
    "text": "Please forgive me, Dr. Heinemann, for \n keeping your daughter out so late."
  },
  {
    "index": 182,
    "start": "0:13:16.46",
    "end": "0:13:18.72",
    "text": "What are you saying, Tenma?"
  },
  {
    "index": 183,
    "start": "0:13:18.72",
    "end": "0:13:21.76",
    "text": "Eva is your fiancé, isn't she?"
  },
  {
    "index": 184,
    "start": "0:13:21.76",
    "end": "0:13:22.89",
    "text": "What do you say?"
  },
  {
    "index": 185,
    "start": "0:13:22.89",
    "end": "0:13:25.10",
    "text": "Would you like to have a cup of tea?"
  },
  {
    "index": 186,
    "start": "0:13:27.43",
    "end": "0:13:31.85",
    "text": "Have you given the wedding \n date to your parents in Japan?"
  },
  {
    "index": 187,
    "start": "0:13:31.85",
    "end": "0:13:33.44",
    "text": "Y-Yes."
  },
  {
    "index": 188,
    "start": "0:13:33.44",
    "end": "0:13:37.15",
    "text": "But my father is only a practitioner in a small hospital..."
  },
  {
    "index": 189,
    "start": "0:13:37.15",
    "end": "0:13:40.03",
    "text": "...so I'm not sure if he can make \n time to come to Germany."
  },
  {
    "index": 190,
    "start": "0:13:40.48",
    "end": "0:13:45.91",
    "text": "It's perfect opportunity, so they\n should enjoy an overseas trip."
  },
  {
    "index": 191,
    "start": "0:13:45.91",
    "end": "0:13:48.91",
    "text": "Yes, since we're the ones who invited them."
  },
  {
    "index": 192,
    "start": "0:13:49.53",
    "end": "0:13:51.33",
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "index": 193,
    "start": "0:13:51.33",
    "end": "0:13:54.41",
    "text": "I'm indebted to you for everything."
  },
  {
    "index": 194,
    "start": "0:13:54.83",
    "end": "0:13:56.87",
    "text": "When you first arrived in Germany..."
  },
  {
    "index": 195,
    "start": "0:13:56.87",
    "end": "0:13:59.33",
    "text": "...I thought you were just some high school kid."
  },
  {
    "index": 196,
    "start": "0:14:00.84",
    "end": "0:14:04.92",
    "text": "But now, you're the number one young surgeon of Eisler Memorial."
  },
  {
    "index": 197,
    "start": "0:14:05.84",
    "end": "0:14:07.63",
    "text": "By the way, Kenzou..."
  },
  {
    "index": 198,
    "start": "0:14:07.63",
    "end": "0:14:13.01",
    "text": "Your current research into cerebral ischemia \n and subarachnoid hemorrhages..."
  },
  {
    "index": 199,
    "start": "0:14:13.39",
    "end": "0:14:17.64",
    "text": "Yes, we're currently making a canine model \n of the subarachnoid hemorrhages."
  },
  {
    "index": 200,
    "start": "0:14:17.64",
    "end": "0:14:20.85",
    "text": "Sorry, but that research has to be canceled."
  },
  {
    "index": 201,
    "start": "0:14:20.85",
    "end": "0:14:21.85",
    "text": "Excuse me?"
  },
  {
    "index": 202,
    "start": "0:14:22.48",
    "end": "0:14:29.23",
    "text": "In the upcoming European Medical Science Symposium, \n I am making a presentation as a speaker."
  },
  {
    "index": 203,
    "start": "0:14:29.23",
    "end": "0:14:32.11",
    "text": "I want you to prepare the manuscripts for me."
  },
  {
    "index": 204,
    "start": "0:14:34.15",
    "end": "0:14:37.78",
    "text": "But... we're near the completion of our research."
  },
  {
    "index": 205,
    "start": "0:14:37.78",
    "end": "0:14:41.08",
    "text": "Man, you should have been there this afternoon."
  },
  {
    "index": 206,
    "start": "0:14:41.08",
    "end": "0:14:43.16",
    "text": "What happened father?"
  },
  {
    "index": 207,
    "start": "0:14:43.16",
    "end": "0:14:47.12",
    "text": "Some suspicious civilian group \n came rushing into the hospital."
  },
  {
    "index": 208,
    "start": "0:14:47.12",
    "end": "0:14:50.88",
    "text": "They made a commotion about the operation we \n performed on the opera singer the other day."
  },
  {
    "index": 209,
    "start": "0:14:50.88",
    "end": "0:14:55.13",
    "text": "They accused us of pushing back the case \n of the Turkish man that came before him."
  },
  {
    "index": 210,
    "start": "0:14:56.97",
    "end": "0:14:59.09",
    "text": "They completely misunderstood the situation."
  },
  {
    "index": 211,
    "start": "0:14:59.09",
    "end": "0:15:02.55",
    "text": "The Turkish man's operation was performed first."
  },
  {
    "index": 212,
    "start": "0:15:02.55",
    "end": "0:15:06.14",
    "text": "There was nothing wrong with our procedures."
  },
  {
    "index": 213,
    "start": "0:15:09.89",
    "end": "0:15:10.81",
    "text": "Isn't that right?"
  },
  {
    "index": 214,
    "start": "0:15:11.31",
    "end": "0:15:13.77",
    "text": "S-Sure..."
  },
  {
    "index": 215,
    "start": "0:15:13.77",
    "end": "0:15:18.32",
    "text": "I swear, they think doctors are some kind of volunteers or something."
  },
  {
    "index": 216,
    "start": "0:15:18.32",
    "end": "0:15:22.36",
    "text": "Even before saving lives, we doctors value academics first."
  },
  {
    "index": 217,
    "start": "0:15:22.36",
    "end": "0:15:23.36",
    "text": "Isn't that right?"
  },
  {
    "index": 218,
    "start": "0:15:27.16",
    "end": "0:15:30.79",
    "text": "In any case, I'll leave the manuscripts \n for my presentation to you."
  },
  {
    "index": 219,
    "start": "0:15:30.79",
    "end": "0:15:34.16",
    "text": "I expect a great deal from you, Tenma."
  },
  {
    "index": 220,
    "start": "0:15:36.46",
    "end": "0:15:38.08",
    "text": "Thank you..."
  },
  {
    "index": 221,
    "start": "0:15:55.35",
    "end": "0:15:56.27",
    "text": "Shit!"
  },
  {
    "index": 222,
    "start": "0:16:08.07",
    "end": "0:16:08.91",
    "text": "Where is the patient?"
  },
  {
    "index": 223,
    "start": "0:16:08.91",
    "end": "0:16:10.24",
    "text": "They have taken him inside."
  },
  {
    "index": 224,
    "start": "0:16:13.54",
    "end": "0:16:14.50",
    "text": "What is his condition?"
  },
  {
    "index": 225,
    "start": "0:16:14.50",
    "end": "0:16:16.83",
    "text": "Blood pressure, 72/50"
  },
  {
    "index": 226,
    "start": "0:16:16.83",
    "end": "0:16:18.87",
    "text": "Pulse, 137."
  },
  {
    "index": 227,
    "start": "0:16:18.87",
    "end": "0:16:21.00",
    "text": "So the bullet entered his skull from the front..."
  },
  {
    "index": 228,
    "start": "0:16:21.71",
    "end": "0:16:23.13",
    "text": "We need X-Rays immediately!"
  },
  {
    "index": 229,
    "start": "0:16:23.13",
    "end": "0:16:24.25",
    "text": "Yes, sir!"
  },
  {
    "index": 230,
    "start": "0:16:27.59",
    "end": "0:16:28.97",
    "text": "Oh, Dr. Tenma!"
  },
  {
    "index": 231,
    "start": "0:16:33.01",
    "end": "0:16:34.05",
    "text": "Who is this girl?"
  },
  {
    "index": 232,
    "start": "0:16:34.05",
    "end": "0:16:36.31",
    "text": "She is the twin sister of that boy just now."
  },
  {
    "index": 233,
    "start": "0:16:36.93",
    "end": "0:16:37.89",
    "text": "Any injuries?"
  },
  {
    "index": 234,
    "start": "0:16:37.89",
    "end": "0:16:39.02",
    "text": "None."
  },
  {
    "index": 235,
    "start": "0:16:39.02",
    "end": "0:16:41.73",
    "text": "It appears she suffered a massive mental shock."
  },
  {
    "index": 236,
    "start": "0:16:47.48",
    "end": "0:16:48.07",
    "text": "What is it?"
  },
  {
    "index": 237,
    "start": "0:16:49.40",
    "end": "0:16:50.57",
    "text": "Kill. Him."
  },
  {
    "index": 238,
    "start": "0:16:56.95",
    "end": "0:16:58.12",
    "text": "Dr. Tenma!"
  },
  {
    "index": 239,
    "start": "0:16:59.58",
    "end": "0:17:02.70",
    "text": "Head shots and CT scans are ready."
  },
  {
    "index": 240,
    "start": "0:17:02.70",
    "end": "0:17:04.58",
    "text": "Okay, I'll be right there."
  },
  {
    "index": 241,
    "start": "0:17:06.12",
    "end": "0:17:09.67",
    "text": "It entered the head from the front, and embedded itself near the center of the brain."
  },
  {
    "index": 242,
    "start": "0:17:10.33",
    "end": "0:17:11.75",
    "text": "Yes..."
  },
  {
    "index": 243,
    "start": "0:17:11.75",
    "end": "0:17:13.67",
    "text": "This will be difficult."
  },
  {
    "index": 244,
    "start": "0:17:16.30",
    "end": "0:17:18.92",
    "text": "The bullet grazed the left side \n of the middle cerebral artery."
  },
  {
    "index": 245,
    "start": "0:17:19.63",
    "end": "0:17:23.26",
    "text": "I see.  Dr. Tenma is right!"
  },
  {
    "index": 246,
    "start": "0:17:23.26",
    "end": "0:17:25.22",
    "text": "This won't be easy."
  },
  {
    "index": 247,
    "start": "0:17:25.22",
    "end": "0:17:27.31",
    "text": "If we move the bullet even a little..."
  },
  {
    "index": 248,
    "start": "0:17:27.52",
    "end": "0:17:30.10",
    "text": "...it might rupture and cause a massive hemorrhage."
  },
  {
    "index": 249,
    "start": "0:17:33.77",
    "end": "0:17:35.31",
    "text": "Sorry, I was late."
  },
  {
    "index": 250,
    "start": "0:17:35.65",
    "end": "0:17:37.23",
    "text": "Dr. Becker!"
  },
  {
    "index": 251,
    "start": "0:17:37.23",
    "end": "0:17:39.94",
    "text": "Why are you late when you're \n supposed to be on duty?!"
  },
  {
    "index": 252,
    "start": "0:17:40.61",
    "end": "0:17:42.74",
    "text": "We'll do a full frontal craniotomy on both sides..."
  },
  {
    "index": 253,
    "start": "0:17:42.74",
    "end": "0:17:44.11",
    "text": "...remove the bone fragments..."
  },
  {
    "index": 254,
    "start": "0:17:44.11",
    "end": "0:17:46.36",
    "text": "...and damaged brain matter as well."
  },
  {
    "index": 255,
    "start": "0:17:46.36",
    "end": "0:17:48.70",
    "text": "We'll then carefully remove the bullet..."
  },
  {
    "index": 256,
    "start": "0:17:48.70",
    "end": "0:17:50.66",
    "text": "...and finally, repair the artery."
  },
  {
    "index": 257,
    "start": "0:17:53.54",
    "end": "0:17:55.71",
    "text": "This operation will take time, but..."
  },
  {
    "index": 258,
    "start": "0:17:55.71",
    "end": "0:17:57.29",
    "text": "Everyone, let's give it our best!"
  },
  {
    "index": 259,
    "start": "0:17:58.96",
    "end": "0:18:00.88",
    "text": "Blood pressure, 120/80."
  },
  {
    "index": 260,
    "start": "0:18:00.88",
    "end": "0:18:02.29",
    "text": "Pulse, 92."
  },
  {
    "index": 261,
    "start": "0:18:02.29",
    "end": "0:18:03.92",
    "text": "Everything looks to be in good condition."
  },
  {
    "index": 262,
    "start": "0:18:03.92",
    "end": "0:18:05.13",
    "text": "Anesthetics administered."
  },
  {
    "index": 263,
    "start": "0:18:14.51",
    "end": "0:18:15.89",
    "text": "Dr. Tenma!"
  },
  {
    "index": 264,
    "start": "0:18:15.89",
    "end": "0:18:16.39",
    "text": "Yes?"
  },
  {
    "index": 265,
    "start": "0:18:17.02",
    "end": "0:18:18.64",
    "text": "This isn't your operation."
  },
  {
    "index": 266,
    "start": "0:18:18.64",
    "end": "0:18:21.60",
    "text": "You must go to Operating Room #1 immediately."
  },
  {
    "index": 267,
    "start": "0:18:22.52",
    "end": "0:18:26.90",
    "text": "The Mayor, Mr. Roedecker, has collapsed \n from a cerebral thrombosis."
  },
  {
    "index": 268,
    "start": "0:18:28.40",
    "end": "0:18:30.57",
    "text": "They're bringing him in by helicopter right now."
  },
  {
    "index": 269,
    "start": "0:18:30.57",
    "end": "0:18:33.11",
    "text": "They should be arriving in ten minutes."
  },
  {
    "index": 270,
    "start": "0:18:33.11",
    "end": "0:18:36.11",
    "text": "Then please contact Dr. Boyer."
  },
  {
    "index": 271,
    "start": "0:18:36.78",
    "end": "0:18:39.24",
    "text": "They're afraid that his artery may be blocked."
  },
  {
    "index": 272,
    "start": "0:18:39.24",
    "end": "0:18:41.66",
    "text": "If that is the case, you must operate on him!"
  },
  {
    "index": 273,
    "start": "0:18:42.83",
    "end": "0:18:47.42",
    "text": "But I was about to start the operation on that child!"
  },
  {
    "index": 274,
    "start": "0:18:51.04",
    "end": "0:18:52.88",
    "text": "It's an order from the director."
  },
  {
    "index": 275,
    "start": "0:18:59.09",
    "end": "0:19:00.76",
    "text": "Yes, this is Tenma."
  },
  {
    "index": 276,
    "start": "0:19:01.51",
    "end": "0:19:05.18",
    "text": "Oh, Tenma.  Please take care of the Mayor's case."
  },
  {
    "index": 277,
    "start": "0:19:05.18",
    "end": "0:19:08.77",
    "text": "I've already contacted Dr. Eisen and Dr. Boyer."
  },
  {
    "index": 278,
    "start": "0:19:08.77",
    "end": "0:19:10.23",
    "text": "This situation should be acceptable, right?"
  },
  {
    "index": 279,
    "start": "0:19:10.23",
    "end": "0:19:14.86",
    "text": "But Director, I was about to start \n on another operation!"
  },
  {
    "index": 280,
    "start": "0:19:14.86",
    "end": "0:19:17.57",
    "text": "Just leave that to Dr. Becker."
  },
  {
    "index": 281,
    "start": "0:19:19.07",
    "end": "0:19:21.03",
    "text": "W-With all due respect, sir!"
  },
  {
    "index": 282,
    "start": "0:19:21.03",
    "end": "0:19:23.20",
    "text": "The patient in the operation I'm about to conduct..."
  },
  {
    "index": 283,
    "start": "0:19:23.20",
    "end": "0:19:25.78",
    "text": "...had a bullet graze the left side of his middle cerebral artery..."
  },
  {
    "index": 284,
    "start": "0:19:25.78",
    "end": "0:19:28.41",
    "text": "...and it'll be a very difficult operation!"
  },
  {
    "index": 285,
    "start": "0:19:28.41",
    "end": "0:19:30.87",
    "text": "However, I'm confident that I can save him."
  },
  {
    "index": 286,
    "start": "0:19:31.66",
    "end": "0:19:34.29",
    "text": "I'm going to leave the Mayor's case to Dr. Boyer."
  },
  {
    "index": 287,
    "start": "0:19:34.29",
    "end": "0:19:37.37",
    "text": "I must operate on the boy for him to survive."
  },
  {
    "index": 288,
    "start": "0:19:38.00",
    "end": "0:19:42.59",
    "text": "Anyway, Tenma, please give everything \n you have to save the Mayor's life."
  },
  {
    "index": 289,
    "start": "0:19:43.42",
    "end": "0:19:46.17",
    "text": "The Mayor has already promised..."
  },
  {
    "index": 290,
    "start": "0:19:46.17",
    "end": "0:19:52.09",
    "text": "...to greatly increase our subsidy \n at the next medical assessment."
  },
  {
    "index": 291,
    "start": "0:19:53.10",
    "end": "0:19:55.81",
    "text": "We can't have him die yet."
  },
  {
    "index": 292,
    "start": "0:19:56.89",
    "end": "0:19:59.31",
    "text": "I'm counting on you, Tenma."
  },
  {
    "index": 293,
    "start": "0:19:59.31",
    "end": "0:20:01.60",
    "text": "I expect a great deal from you."
  },
  {
    "index": 294,
    "start": "0:20:04.19",
    "end": "0:20:05.27",
    "text": "Yes, sir..."
  },
  {
    "index": 295,
    "start": "0:20:09.98",
    "end": "0:20:11.86",
    "text": "The Mayor has arrived at the heliport!"
  },
  {
    "index": 296,
    "start": "0:20:12.95",
    "end": "0:20:15.61",
    "text": "Get to angio immediately after the CT."
  },
  {
    "index": 297,
    "start": "0:20:15.61",
    "end": "0:20:17.66",
    "text": "Please confirm which areas are blocked."
  },
  {
    "index": 298,
    "start": "0:20:24.12",
    "end": "0:20:27.25",
    "text": "Hey, you better make preparations, Dr. Tenma."
  },
  {
    "index": 299,
    "start": "0:20:27.25",
    "end": "0:20:30.54",
    "text": "We're relying on those brilliant skills of yours."
  },
  {
    "index": 300,
    "start": "0:20:35.05",
    "end": "0:20:38.72",
    "text": "They think doctors are some kind of \n volunteers or something..."
  },
  {
    "index": 301,
    "start": "0:20:39.59",
    "end": "0:20:44.60",
    "text": "Even before saving lives, we doctors \n value academics first."
  },
  {
    "index": 302,
    "start": "0:20:44.60",
    "end": "0:20:47.06",
    "text": "Isn't that right?"
  },
  {
    "index": 303,
    "start": "0:20:47.06",
    "end": "0:20:52.31",
    "text": "I merely operated on that opera singer \n like the director told me to."
  },
  {
    "index": 304,
    "start": "0:20:52.31",
    "end": "0:20:53.90",
    "text": "It is not my fault."
  },
  {
    "index": 305,
    "start": "0:20:53.90",
    "end": "0:20:55.77",
    "text": "Of course."
  },
  {
    "index": 306,
    "start": "0:20:55.77",
    "end": "0:20:59.07",
    "text": "Because people's lives aren't equal."
  },
  {
    "index": 307,
    "start": "0:21:02.32",
    "end": "0:21:04.28",
    "text": "Give him back!"
  },
  {
    "index": 308,
    "start": "0:21:04.82",
    "end": "0:21:08.08",
    "text": "If only you had operated on him, he would have survived!"
  },
  {
    "index": 309,
    "start": "0:21:08.08",
    "end": "0:21:16.00",
    "text": "Give him back!  Give him back!"
  },
  {
    "index": 310,
    "start": "0:21:19.92",
    "end": "0:21:21.71",
    "text": "What is wrong, Dr. Tenma?"
  },
  {
    "index": 311,
    "start": "0:21:27.72",
    "end": "0:21:28.76",
    "text": "I..."
  },
  {
    "index": 312,
    "start": "0:21:30.43",
    "end": "0:21:32.26",
    "text": "I have an operation waiting for me in there."
  },
  {
    "index": 313,
    "start": "0:21:35.56",
    "end": "0:21:37.52",
    "text": "H-Hey, Dr. Tenma!"
  },
  {
    "index": 314,
    "start": "0:21:37.98",
    "end": "0:21:40.14",
    "text": "This is an order from the director!"
  },
  {
    "index": 315,
    "start": "0:21:40.14",
    "end": "0:21:42.85",
    "text": "The Mayor is currently having a CT scan done on him."
  },
  {
    "index": 316,
    "start": "0:21:42.85",
    "end": "0:21:45.06",
    "text": "All doctors, please report to the trace-reading \n room immediately."
  },
  {
    "index": 317,
    "start": "0:21:45.06",
    "end": "0:21:45.73",
    "text": "Okay!"
  },
  {
    "index": 318,
    "start": "0:21:46.19",
    "end": "0:21:48.15",
    "text": "Wait, Dr. Tenma!"
  },
  {
    "index": 319,
    "start": "0:21:48.15",
    "end": "0:21:49.65",
    "text": "Dr. Tenma!"
  },
  {
    "index": 320,
    "start": "0:21:59.37",
    "end": "0:22:00.79",
    "text": "You'll be okay."
  },
  {
    "index": 321,
    "start": "0:22:00.79",
    "end": "0:22:02.16",
    "text": "Hang in there!"
  },
  {
    "index": 322,
    "start": "0:22:02.16",
    "end": "0:22:04.33",
    "text": "I'll save you!"
  },
  {
    "index": 323,
    "start": "0:22:19.39",
    "end": "0:22:21.26",
    "text": "Kill... him...."
  },
  {
    "index": 324,
    "start": "0:22:23.64",
    "end": "0:22:25.22",
    "text": "Kill... him...."
  }
]